        <item>
            <title>Red Hat：當前人工智慧主要還是強化現有功能，還要 3-5 年才會有明顯爆發情況</title>
            <description>&lt;p&gt;今年 5 月在丹佛舉辦的技術大會中公佈以開源形式加速推動自動生成式&lt;a class=&quot;link &quot; href=&quot;https://tw.news.yahoo.com/tag/%E4%BA%BA%E5%B7%A5%E6%99%BA%E6%85%A7&quot; data-i13n=&quot;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link&quot; data-ylk=&quot;slk:人工智慧;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0&quot;&gt;人工智慧&lt;/a&gt;成長的&lt;a data-i13n=&quot;cpos:1;pos:1&quot; href=&quot;https://mashdigi.com/red-hat-releases-red-hat-enterprise-linux-ai-service-platform-to-accelerate-the-growth-of-automatically-generated-artificial-intelligence-in-an-open-source-form/&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-ylk=&quot;slk:Red Hat Enterprise Linux AI 服務平台;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas&quot; class=&quot;link &quot;&gt;Red Hat Enterprise Linux AI 服務平台&lt;/a&gt;，並且更新&lt;a data-i13n=&quot;cpos:2;pos:1&quot; href=&quot;https://mashdigi.com/red-hat-updates-ansible-automation-platform-to-enable-artificial-intelligence-to-operate-in-accordance-with-specific-principles-in-hybrid-cloud-environments/&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-ylk=&quot;slk:Ansible 自動化平台;cpos:2;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas&quot; class=&quot;link &quot;&gt;Ansible 自動化平台&lt;/a&gt;，讓人工智慧可在&lt;a data-i13n=&quot;cpos:3;pos:1&quot; href=&quot;https://mashdigi.com/red-hat-expands-openshift-ai-platform-resource-application-integration-scope-to-accelerate-artificial-intelligence-deployment-applications-across-hybrid-cloud-infrastructure/&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-ylk=&quot;slk:混合雲環境;cpos:3;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas&quot; class=&quot;link &quot;&gt;混合雲環境&lt;/a&gt;以符合特定原則運作，Red Hat 今日 (11/5) 活動上表示未來的人工智慧技術發展將建構在混合雲環境下成長，而混合雲架構也將使人工智慧能輕易佈署於任何場景使用。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;figure class=&quot;caas-figure&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;caas-figure-with-pb&quot;&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;caas-img-container caas-img-loader&